msgstr "those you should frequent, and those you shouldn’t frequent."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an9.6:3.1"
msgid "‘Puggalopi, āvuso, duvidhena veditabbo—"
msgstr "You should distinguish two kinds of people:"

msgctxt "an9.6:3.2"
msgid "sevitabbopi asevitabbopī’ti, "
msgstr ""
"those you should associate with, and those you shouldn’t associate with.’ "

msgctxt "an9.6:3.3"
msgid "iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ. Kiñcetaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ?"
msgstr "That’s what I said, but why did I say it?"

msgctxt "an9.6:3.4"
msgid "Tattha yaṃ jaññā puggalaṃ:"
msgstr "Take a person of whom you know this."

msgctxt "an9.6:3.5"
msgid ""
"‘imaṃ kho me puggalaṃ sevato akusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti, kusalā dhammā "
"parihāyanti;"
msgstr ""
"‘When I associate with this person, unskillful qualities grow, and "
"skillful qualities decline."

msgctxt "an9.6:3.6"
msgid ""
"ye ca kho me pabbajitena jīvitaparikkhārā samudānetabbā "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārā te ca kasirena "
"samudāgacchanti;"
msgstr ""
"And the necessities of life that a renunciate requires—robes, alms-food, "
"lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick—are hard to come by."

msgctxt "an9.6:3.7"
msgid ""
"yassa camhi atthāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito so ca me sāmaññattho na "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchatī’ti, tenāvuso, puggalena so puggalo rattibhāgaṃ vā "
"divasabhāgaṃ vā saṅkhāpi anāpucchā pakkamitabbaṃ nānubandhitabbo."
msgstr ""
"And the goal of the ascetic life for which I went forth from the lay life "
"to homelessness is not being developed to perfection.’ In this case you "
"should leave that person at that very time of the day or night, without "
"asking. You shouldn’t follow them."

